{"tid":1238630,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔叫林鄭落台一定要吹到係我地釋出善意","createTime":"2019-06-18T01:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T06:56:22.000Z","uid":81424,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1bde32d6b49ac2bce6186b33da043018fcbebb65","tid":1238630,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:30:53.000Z","msg":"叫林鄭落台百害而無一利<br />\n一嚟少咗個集氣對象<br />\n二嚟學班親中派話齋  佢落台再整個689 3.0咩<br />\n三嚟林鄭威信全失 已經好難再禍港 新特首就有機會禍港<br />\n四嚟仲可以吹到係我地釋出善意 回應林鄭所謂嘅善意 一人讓一步 爭取民意<br />\n<br />\n認同請推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1475a9e7309625025b3f3210dc503319cb0417","tid":1238630,"uid":81424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:49:53.000Z","msg":"達成四項訴求 <br />\n清算醫管局<br />\n同推倒明日大嶼同國歌法之前<br />\n<br />\n林鄭仲未落得台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa2fc88d2342756b3718e941ee1678911b3cb98","tid":1238630,"uid":81424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yOYuO6P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOYuO6P.jpg&h=c26134dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da7faacec8d065f91c01782f6be219446ae84e6d","tid":1238630,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:54:02.000Z","msg":"但問題自己重想做, 佢唔走吹佢唔漲"},{"pid":"d35433af1858640e27d66cf493b1e4f1ebf856db","tid":1238630,"uid":151321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:59:39.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"c19c5c42bcabc34695ec0981d026213834a13dc4","tid":1238630,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:01:07.000Z","msg":"林鄭落唔落台係北京決定<br />\n你對北京釋出善意把撚咩"},{"pid":"64ecf89334188d2b89a08335641897237437e1d4","tid":1238630,"uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c19c5c42bcabc34695ec0981d026213834a13dc4","tid":1238630,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"